    },
    {
      "title": "Our AI Research: How We Evaluate Semantic Search Technology",
      "url": "https://exa.ai/blog/evals-at-exa",
      "description": "We can use SimpleQA, where an LLM agent must answer factual questions using search results. We pass each question to an LLM, which calls the ...",
